🚨CHEESY post incoming 🚨

I am super grateful for EVERY one of you who have supported me on this journey of becoming a full time DJ 🙏

Making the transition from software engineer to DJ was definitely not easy.  For one, I lost the stability that came with having a full time job. 

HOWEVER. The passion I have for music, and allowing me to share it with you all is what keeps me going every day. 💪

I wouldn't be anywhere close to where I'm currently at without each and every one of you 🫶

The BEST moments of every night is when both the crowd and I are in sync, absolutely vibing to the same song.🔥

It's true what they say - music brings people together and unites us.

2022 is just the beginning. Bring it on, 2023! 👊

Pioneer’s newest DDJ-FLX series comes with some new features, one of the most notable being the Smart Fader Function.

The Smart Fader function allows for hands-free control of the volume, bass, and BPM simultaneously. This allows you to easily switch between songs with only a swipe of the channel faders or crossfader.

Learning the fundamentals of DJing and other mixing techniques will be much easier with this great new feature on the Pioneer DDJ-FLX4 DJ Controller.
